title: 이달의소녀탐구 #507 (LOONA TV #507)
summary:
The episode starts off with snippets of some solos in the MV. The MV shoot ends and they all thank the staff.
0:23 -- The group celebrates the successful end of the shoot. They were on for 24 hours according to HaSeul.
0:31 -- Kim Lip talks about the dresses and how pretty they were.
